Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.05,0:01:32.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,600)}{\pos(345,262)}奈莎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙露奈大人 芙露奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 芙露奈大人到底去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都鎮定點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭司長大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能說她「去哪兒了」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是哪兒也去不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在這個世界裡 一切都是相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她回來了 得好好懲罰她才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢偷走世界的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咚——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是抱歉 忘記先打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷…因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接嶄新的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 克雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…電子分身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過感覺好逼真…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要摸摸我的頭看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 別客氣 摸我的頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 能摸得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 很不可思議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎也不是很明白自己啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎真是不可思議呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你和芙露奈什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙露奈?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她把你丟在這裡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把奈莎丟下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙露奈她…是討厭奈莎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不 應該不會的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎討厭討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎喜歡喜歡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嘭嚓嚓 嘭嚓嚓 若向白晝的星辰獻上心願」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}她不是芙露奈的電子分身嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}感覺是個靜不下來的怪女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}不對 要說怪 芙露奈也不輸她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因 怎麼又換了個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是昨天那個女孩落在這裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落在這裡的? 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好可愛!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠觸摸到電子分身?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒錯 這孩子不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說了嘛 是她落在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話得趕緊還給她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的話就交到警察那兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是別人落下的東西吧 所以就得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看! 超大型髪帶!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算說去還 可我也不知道芙露奈在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 有小鳥 好像很舒服耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎很喜歡小鳥喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 芙露奈喜不喜歡小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙露奈啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到她之後怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要發火!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風好舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹過臉頰 感覺癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂動啦 不然會掉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 叫你別亂動的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 反正你也只是電子分身 應該沒事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸你…幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快摸摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸得到 摸得到誒!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的摸得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼這麼冷清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 發現一位大叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是什麼都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶只有部門設施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是警察局 機關什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然房子很多 但裡面都沒人住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎 你待在我家也沒什麼用…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是提個建議啦 要不你就在這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大的鐘喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不可以隨便就跑進去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊奈莎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多車誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是來這兒玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那些房車是他們的家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話無拘無束 十分方便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算星星掉下來 也能隨時轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是中轉基地啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在城鎮周圍 信號也更穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有家的話人更輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是克雷因就有家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛…因為比較喜歡舊東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總是被媽媽說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒有等著他們回去的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有家 在家等你回去的也不過是電子分身而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本人就是無拘無束的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 也沒有必要去用家來束縛自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太神速了吧 你就不能給我老實一點嗎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不見了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐吶 那個比被人摸摸頭還要開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 在這裡睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道廁所會在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 居然跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說喔 奈莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小寶寶好開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得小酒窩都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先聽我講啦 奈莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈 飛起來了 飛起來了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看上去都好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪他 把這裡搞得亂七八糟!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們兩個 快賠錢!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次被人弄得這樣陣腳大亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才玩得好開心喔 克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 接下來咱們去哪兒玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去把你交給警察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能再跟你一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎會和克雷因在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是奈莎的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克雷因呼喚出奈莎的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以克雷因在哪裡 奈莎的家就在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 奈莎的笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我如此害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因…摸不到奈莎了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去警察局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你說她是別人落下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先保管著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜 克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該了吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你偷了我們的零件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這叫以牙還牙  以 牙 還 牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把他帶來了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛! 到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個巫女給藏起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了就自己跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色 色 色魔!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一起待到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個不折不扣的色魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我消毒!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再問你 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張口閉口的「少年」 你自己不也是少年嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才露營地的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你鬧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是我 是芙露奈的電子分身…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是我不知道她現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道又亂跑到哪裡去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大騙子! 你絕對知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個超級大色魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定連這樣那樣的事情都知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口一個色魔的 你煩不煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我根本就不是色魔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作也好 運動也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些麻煩事電子分身都會替我們做好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己親身感受到的體驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種衝擊是無可比擬的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「你可以回去了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就被跟蹤了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道他們還真以為沒被我發現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正芙露奈也走了 奈莎也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間屋子 原來有這麼大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有自己的電子分身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很抵觸有另外一個自己存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才不想被那傢伙那樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可觸摸 電子分身…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來早就有研發了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然奈莎是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…描繪電子分身的計算機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運算出壓力和質感…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為性愛玩具…在黑市上交易…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我不就真的成色魔了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 要實現觸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須向體內的納米裝置傳輸該電子分身的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳輸數據?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有話想跟你談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間就別互相瞞著對方什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什麼苦惱 希望你能告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽會和你一起想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子 總覺得…你有點反常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去些奇怪的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶女孩子回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦 芙露奈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽是因為相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才准你住在家裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你自己能夠更自覺一點 克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼在意我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接在這裡一起生活不就結了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直瞎說 這樣的話不就等於限制了自由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為相互間深入理解 所以彼此都能自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才是家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一家人都住在同一間屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就證明彼此間沒有信賴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是克雷因呼喚出奈莎的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以克雷因在哪裡 奈莎的家就在哪裡」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就是因為很重視你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸媽媽才會用電子分身這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就是想自己隨心所欲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因 果然你不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前從來不會這樣頂撞父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是因為爸爸媽媽的電子分身出故障了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我今天一直在跑個不停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有什麼會蹦出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣一路奔跑 感覺有什麼會脫口而出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我變成了孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正發火的對象 不應該是爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我心裡很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為覺得煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被弄得陣腳大亂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 才把奈莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.58,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}8點的禱告時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:53.33,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}基於你現在的所在地 修道院的方位是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:56.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}右前方約20度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼禱告啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是在收集我的數據而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}來 虔誠地祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「若向白晝的星辰獻上心願」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是見到芙露奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是向奈莎道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明白 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭 我討厭孤零零地一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莎的笑容 一點都不令人害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷因 我回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅一點都不令人害怕 甚至…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 克雷因身上好暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話應該我說才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是如此的一目瞭然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寶箱誒 克雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 等等 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當了吧 大白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況算上當嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擺了一道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥計們 回收獵物!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 飛起來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------OPJP-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:22.91,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}捨てたはずの不安の種が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:28.28,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}心を突き破って芽を出した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:37.09,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}無数のいばらが今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:44.31,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}足下伸びて待ち構えている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:52.83,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}どこへゆけば会える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:01:07.60,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}抱きしめないで 背中のトゲは 君を傷付けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:22.97,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}それでも 溢れる想いが 君を探している
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------------OPCN-----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:22.91,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}本應早已捨弃的不安之種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:28.28,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}衝破心靈的土壤開始萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:37.09,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}數不清的荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:44.31,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}依舊深扎在前方嚴陣以待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:52.83,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}要去往何方才能與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:01:07.60,ed_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}不要擁抱我 我背上的銳刺會傷害到你
